# Corporate CA Certificate — Example / Placeholder
#
# How to use:
#   1. Export your corporate CA certificate in PEM format (see docs/guides/ace-tls.md)
#   2. Copy this file to corp-ca.pem in the same directory:
#        cp admin-editor/certs/corp-ca.pem.example admin-editor/certs/corp-ca.pem
#   3. Replace this placeholder content with your actual certificate.
#   4. Restart ACE (npm run admin).
#
# The file admin-editor/certs/corp-ca.pem is .gitignored — it will not be committed.
# The .example file is committed as a guide.
#
# Multiple certificates: you may concatenate multiple PEM blocks in one file.
#
# Example certificate format (replace with your actual cert):
#
# -----BEGIN CERTIFICATE-----
# MIIDXTCCAkWgAwIBAgIJALfRlWsI8YQHMA0GCSqGSIb3DQEBBQUAMEUxCzAJBgNV
# BAYTAlVTMRMwEQYDVQQIDApTb21lLVN0YXRlMSEwHwYDVQQKDBhJbnRlcm5ldCBX
# aWRnaXRzIFB0eSBMdGQwHhcNMTgwNDI0MTUzMTE5WhcNMTkwNDI0MTUzMTE5WjBF
# MQswCQYDVQQGEwJVUzETMBEGA1UECAwKU29tZS1TdGF0ZTEhMB8GA1UECgwYSW50
# ZXJuZXQgV2lkZ2l0cyBQdHkgTHRkMIIBIjANBgkqhkiG9w0BAQEFAAOCAQ8AMIIB
# CgKCAQEA2a2rwplBQLF29amygykEMmYz0+Kcj3bKBp29P2rFj7FBMSzD0cMY2EGN
# GnGMNOABNRHbGGQFMGYiWIhGrSJdV/+aOl1r+z0gNjbMzBVSfS8bBlIoH6cPqES
# ZcmpSVBIRGITVbJLCVwRjAfm1aXEjB8HqTybwqQGtGFkXPJZzjFBaGMdPlzJz3V9
# P2YNlE0rKZUWC4ZMTKx2VoqFCCZSYaLfBjX1IAoMI7o4zezxCBJXQTkiSvI3kJ6G
# ...
# -----END CERTIFICATE-----
